attachments.title: Buffer Community on Slack
attachments.text: Thank you for your interest in joining our community on Slack! Buffer's community on Slack is a supportive and positive space for social media marketers and enthusiasts to discuss the latest in social media and marketing, help and learn from one another, and meaningfully connect on a deeper level. If this sounds like something you want to be part of, we'd love to invite you to join in! We go through every application to learn more about you so as to provide the most value to you and the community. If you aren't a Buffer user, we would love to encourage you to try it out! We have a free version you can sign up for at <http://www.buffer.com|www.buffer.com>. :)
